## The Agenda: Acceleration and Alignment

So let us get right down to what we may call an agenda. You may entitle this "agenda." The idea simply is that many individuals have sensed, taken readings of the overall energy of your society and how you are progressing in your assimilation of data, in your assimilation and application of information, of your own awareness of Consciousness. You have created a momentum that is pushing you faster and faster and faster towards certain things. Many of you already beginning to see physical effects not only in your own individual lives but on a planetary scale.

Now, the idea of your focus on peace—all of your walls and barriers seem to be coming down, both figuratively and literally, and we congratulate you all. It has made us most happy to see this begin. Many of us communicating through many of you have talked about certain times that are specific points of acceleration. The last time that I spoke with you in this particular area, I spoke about the date October 15th. And after that date, there will be much acceleration in a certain way. Allow me now to explain in a little more detail what exactly is meant.

As you begin to choose the lives, the paths, the attitudes, and the habits that are now more representative of peace and creativity, as you begin to choose these things, you begin to crystallize the events of your life in certain specific ways to allow only certain types of opportunity, certain types of situations to occur—what we call positive synchronicity. What you put out is what you give back, as we have said many times. As we have accelerated this, it becomes less and less likely, in fact more and more difficult, to choose anything that is not representative of what you really desire, of what you really prefer.

You find now that this October 15th date was given to indicate a smash point that you have crossed, where you have created enough individuals in your society aiming for what they desire, so that should you for any reason whatsoever—doubt, fear, hesitation, habit—begin to choose that which is not what you desire, it would begin to fall apart more quickly to point you in the proper direction by not working out, by creating more and more unhappy, stressful situations in the things that you no longer want to do, to make you tired more quickly of those things, to give you signs more strongly that those are not the things that you are all about as an individual.

Therefore, from that day forward, you will find that the more you hesitate to do the things that you really know you are all about, the things that really excite you, the less well things will go for you, the more confusion there will be in your life in a negative sense.

## The 1990-1993 Timeline

Agenda now is approximately that between your time now of 1990 and 1992 or three, more and more of this energy will crystallize. I know that I will be very bold in the statement, and understand that this is simply how we are perceiving your energy at this time, but the momentum is very strong, so I will make the statement anyway.

If you have not by 1993 allowed yourself to do in your lives only what is really representative on any level of what you prefer, what you desire to be, from that point forward you may not be able to catch up. The acceleration will be so great at that point that if you are not allowing yourself to be aligned with your own truth, you may find it—almost nothing is impossible, but almost impossible to backtrack without absolute breakdown of everything you know.

For the next three of your years, you can do it somewhat smoothly with some buffers and some timing and some pacing. If you have not allowed yourself to crystallize in what is really important to you by your 1993, the only way it may be available to you to do so will be to completely cut yourself off from everything and start, as you say, from scratch. Now some people might find this more exciting—that will be up to you. I am not telling you what to do, just giving you a reading of your energy because that is how fast you are acting, that is how fast you are changing.

There is no reason to hesitate, there is no reason to delay to do what you really want to do, and there is no reason to hold on to those jobs, those situations, those relationships that are not representative of you. Allow them to change gracefully. Change them gracefully with integrity, with love, but change them. Do not fear your typical fears: "I cannot quit my job, what will I do? What will I eat? How will I live? Where will I live? I will not be able to pay the rent. I will be kicked out." Trust once again—and I will only say this briefly because I have already said it enough—trust once again that the thing in life that excites you the most comes complete with all the tools necessary to support you in the doing of that thing. It is automatic, it is built in. All you need to do is act on the opportunities that doing that situation brings to you.

